projectGridLines.title: Using Alternatives to transform Sustainable processes
projectGridLines.description:
Description: A lot of industries today use more harmful parts in their processes.

The aim is to find how existing research can be used to change this to a more

sustainable approach

Skill sets: Excel, En-Roads, Core knowledge

Traits expectation: Passionate to learn

Expected learning: Student will be able to use existing material available and adapt

to industry usage

Specific courses required for project execution: HSS F381: Environmental

Sustainability Ventures
